messages.text: You wouldn’t answer my regular number…
I just thought… How we left things…
whose number are you txting from??
We haven’t spoken since you broke up with me…
So excuse me if things are done a little unconventionally…
ha. you’re sick, you know that.
Come on… After all we’ve been through…
I left for a reason Bern.
now you’re not helping your case.
txting me from a foreign phone, demanding we see each other.
Sorry if you mistake my love for weirdness.
you have no idea what love is.
that’s not something you tell your ex…
Sometimes love makes you do stupid stuff.
how could you think I’d come meet you?!?
I’ll buy you your favorite drink.
Why do you hurt me so much…
after all you’ve done and I have to apologize.
Come to Mays…OR I can come to your house…
you better not come anywhere near my house.
I’ll do what I have to…
I will call the cops if you come
I just wanna chance to explain myself…
I gave you that chance, but you just shrugged it away.
which is weird that you’re insistent now.
you didn’t care before and now you’re going to great lengths to contact me…
Love makes you do strange things.
my dad has a gun…I will use it
Are you that fed up with me?!?!
I just don’t like how you’re inviting yourself
and txting me  from an unknown number
and just now, a week after our breakup, txting me
Is that you Donna? or Minka?
you can quit the act now.
I know this is a joke.
wow guys… a bit cruel for it being so close to the breakup.
seriously guys, you can quit the act.
And now I’m pretty pissed you think it is.
I don’t like how you’re mocking me.
why do you keep playing?! I know it’s one of you guys.
Bern, why are you txting me…?
at least some who said they were you…
Do u know wat they wanted from u?!
R u goin to meet them?!?
K. Good. Where did they say they were at?
they-well, you said you were coming here…
whoever is txting me said they were coming to my house.
wait… He looks just like you…
No time 2 explain. Just get away.
Is this part of the joke!?
NO!! STOP, DON’T ANSWER THE DOOR.
I’m gonna give you a piece of my mind…
Wat have u done with her?!?
Nah, I think I’ll keep her.
She’s the last piece to the puzzle. Not complete without her.
